Package com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.object.specialized Description

Contains specialized versions of Either. For either of object or primitive, only right side is specialized (in other words, if you want an Either instance that holds either X or Y (where Y is primitive) you will have only right side specialized for those primitives values). For either of primitive values, neither sides can have same primitive type. Note: all classes are generated by YTemplate (a project that I have not released yet).
